String.string: <font size='50'>Absorbing the warden is making Banyakas unstable!</font>
<font size='50'>Banyakas becomes calm when the Dominolith is destroyed.</font>
<font size='50'>I have regained enough power to destroy the coercive shard!</font>
<font size='50'>I am too injured to move. You must protect me.</font>
<font size='50'>Banyakas sustains a serious injury and stops moving.</font>
<font size='50'>As the coercive shard shatters, the mad sporewalker appears.</font>
<font size='50'>I'm all right. Go help the petralisks.</font>
<font size='50'>Thank you for helping me. You must help Banyakas.</font>
The last of Banyakas's wardens is about to be enthralled. We have to do something.
Can you protect the Guardian while he recovers? He's behind me. Hurry!
<font size='50'>The dark wardens collapse as the hypnotic stone is destroyed.</font>
<font size='30'>Now that the Dominolith is shattered, Banyakas should soon return to his senses.</font>
<font size='30'>Thank you for protecting our forest. Let me give you this small gift on Banyakas's behalf.</font>
<font size='30'>Now that the Dominolith is shattered and Banyakas is injured, he will soon return to his senses.</font>
<font size='30'>Allow me to present you with this small gift on Banyakas's behalf.</font>
<font size='30'>Even with their minds enchanted, the Gatekeeper and Guardian tried to protect Banyakas. They will be missed.</font>
